snippet.textDisplay: Can someone explain this to me because this is something that confuses me most about Scottish football... Why is that Hamilton away end not full? Surely playing Rangers or Celtic is like a cup final to these other clubs in the league. It's not just away followings though, I always see loads of empty seats in the home end when Celtic and Rangers come to town, I just wanna know why this is.
